# Document Development Tools

When any of these scenarios occur, use the `document-dev-tools` skill:

## Trigger Scenarios

- User adds, removes, or modifies MCP servers
- User creates, updates, or removes skills
- User asks about available tools, MCPs, or capabilities
- User requests to update or generate `DEVELOPMENTTOOLS.md`
- User sets up a new development environment

## Action

1. Read and follow `.cursor/skills/document-dev-tools/SKILL.md`
2. Update `.cursor/DEVELOPMENTTOOLS.md` with current state

## Keywords

Listen for: "MCP", "tools", "skills", "agents", "capabilities", "what can you do", "DEVELOPMENTTOOLS"
